Saga 11 is an award winning music production company specializing in recording and producing music, high quality musicians, live music, arts and cultural events for the US and Latinamerica, as well as providing music and performing arts classes.
Saga 11 Productions was established in 2010. Music, culture, love, passion, excellence, precision, and service, all together in a company that became the path to distinction and greatness to those who serves.
